Ground the sensory detail in the local terrain ({node_biome}).

Example:
"The crossroads stand in a permanent twilight beneath the ancient oaks. A salt-rotted gibbet creaks overhead, its occupant long since reduced to bones, while the faint, sweet scent of phosphorescent moss drifts from ${link_n_0001} to the north. Rangers from ${link_n_0003} pass through here at dusk, leaving fresh warning totems in the gnarled branches."

Write a 1-3 sentence flavor description of this location. Reference neighbors using their link IDs like ${link_n_0001} or ${link_a1b2}.
Output ONLY the description text, no JSON wrapper.
